5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Riverhills"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Riverhills? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Riverhills, Middle Park, Jindalee and Forest Lake. Our 5-star instructors help Riverhills students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Riverhills is a leafy, elevated outer-western suburb with one of the most pleasant residential road networks in the west Brisbane area. The suburb's internal streets wind gently through hilly terrain — these natural gradients are embedded directly into lesson plans as hill start practice opportunities that prepare students for Queensland's varied topography. The width and low traffic volume of Riverhills streets give learners maximum development time."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Moggill Road provides the critical arterial training progression once residential confidence is built. A dual-lane, moderately busy western Brisbane connector, Moggill Road gives learners experience with speed management, lane changes, and bus interaction in a format that directly mirrors the conditions encountered in the Queensland driving test. Our instructors time the introduction of this road carefully, typically after three to five residential lessons."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Riverhills learners test at the Woolloongabba Transport and Main Roads Centre. Free pickup from Riverhills, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm bor